msgid "Register Payments"
msgstr "Zarejestruj płatności"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:443
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`journal entries <payroll/in-journal>` are validated, Odoo "
"can generate payments."
msgstr ""
"Po zatwierdzeniu :ref:`zapisów dziennika <payroll/in-journal>`, Odoo może "
"wygenerować płatności."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:445
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:500
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:392
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:412
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:533
msgid ""
"Payments can be :guilabel:`Grouped by Partner` if there is a partner "
"associated with a salary rule."
msgstr ""
"Płatności mogą być :guilabel:`Pogrupowane według partnera`, jeśli z regułą "
"płacową powiązany jest partner."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/india.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:None
